><![CDATA[DogeLshibee]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Now I gotta beat the 50/50 in 5 years... but we're getting there.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xHNoMy3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4u0QTCN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Last Valentine's Day sucked. Dying sucked too. But as of 1123 PM last night I made it through the year that was supposed to kill me.

The struggling to breathe, the inability to walk, take a shower... it really sucked. The pain of learning to stand, learning to wheel around... walking? It all sucked.  Every moment was a new learned pain, and a little triumph knowing that as long as I hurt? I was beating the alternative. 

And so I sit here, listening to the Mountain Goats This Year, wondering if the luck will keep going. Still stuck in a chair for periods, progress is slow and steady but it's winning the race.  Thanks for those who have kept in contact and checking on me.  I hope all is well for you and yours, and that you have a great day!

Dovie'andi se tovya sagain, 

-The Librarian</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xHNoMy3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MidnightLibrarian]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How conservatives see the world:</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CeUV6zK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NyBek8T.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CeUV6zK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ButtBot9900]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cake day dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nWyp7ef</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rj5m3hd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V6iz5X3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GJ2GSPq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Really hoping this uploads with sound, the little icon disappeared halfway though making the post</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BJ7h7dv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s73RSvu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eHt1zw2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I cropped the TikTok ending, you're gonna have to live with the watermark.

